trength that women and girls have.\\\"\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"the same heart\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"noise\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"a boxer\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the strength\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her fighting style, characterised by relentless aggression, strategic body shots, and close-range combat combinations, embodies the quintessential Mexican boxing tradition.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\", \"score\": 0.9995603216801288, \"rank\": 0.00024080339884070034, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her fighting style\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"relentless aggression\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"strategic body shots\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"close-range combat combinations\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This tradition, forged in neighbourhood gyms across Mexico, has produced scores of great fighters like Salvador Sanchez, Julio Cesar Chavez and Canelo Alvarez.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2549, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999999988835953, \"rank\": 1.1162243955594398e-09, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 2600, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salvador_S\\u00e1nchez\", \"score\": 0.9